   <topic>API_GETUSERNAME Function</topic>
   <syntax>Name_String as C = API_GetUserName()</syntax>
   <description>Returns the name of Windows logon name of the current user</description>
   <discussion>
API_GETUSERNAME() returns the name of the current user.
Limitations: Desktop applications only.
   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
? API_GETUSERNAME()
= "ALincoln"
]]></example>
   
